    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Courier",
        "Description": "Terrible news, 47. An agent has been murdered and a classified report was taken from his body.\r\rAn old friend accidentally purchased this stolen document believing it to contain information about terrorists.\r\rIn the meantime, a Swiss banker named Hunsicker, a middle-man in this affair, has offered to return his money.\r\rI want you to go to him, discover who killed our agent, and collect the money.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as The Elite Institute.",
